          <v-card-text class="subheading" v-if="false">
            <p>We are very sad to announce that the #R62Rally2022 has had to be cancelled once again.</p>
            <p>To all our loyal rally-goers and fellow riders, we know that you will be as disappointed as we are.</p>
            <p>Even though this is a sign of the times, and probably not a shock to most; we really were doing everything in our power to make it happen. Against all odds.</p>
